# DeelMarkt — License allowlist
#
# Closes Tier-1 retrospective B-60. Companion to
# scripts/check_dependencies_pana.dart.
#
# Purpose: explicit, auditable record of any third-party dependency whose
# license is otherwise on the blocklist (GPL / AGPL / CC-BY-NC / SSPL but
# is permitted in this codebase under a documented rationale.
#
# Format:  <package_name>:<spdx_license_id>:<rationale>
# Lines starting with `#` are comments. Blank lines ignored.
#
# CHANGE PROCESS:
#   1. Adding an entry → requires reso/belengaz license + GDPR sign-off
#      review on the PR (CLAUDE.md §13 hard-gate analogue for licenses).
#   2. Rationale MUST cite (a) why the dep is needed and (b) why a
#      permissively-licensed alternative is not viable.
#   3. Removing an entry → no review beyond standard PR review (a removed
#      allowlist entry tightens the gate).
#
# CURRENT STATE (2026-04-30):
#   No entries. The scanner has not yet found any blocked-class license
#   in the resolved dependency tree on origin/dev. This file exists as
#   the documented escape hatch for any future exception.
#
# Reference: Tier-1 retrospective B-60, scripts/check_dependencies_pana.dart
